{
  "stem": "24470.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't respond to that very well.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I call it helping children grow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was working as a teacher-director, first as a teacher, then as a teacher-director in a small nursery school.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And had a wonderful program which I developed myself, which I'm writing about now, to describe my work.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As a teacher I worked 35 years.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--and director.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In particular school, for 25.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[DRINKS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I-- I think it's extremely important for many reasons.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "First of all-- [RINGING] --to leave-- that's not ours.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "To leave testimony of what we went through, although there are people that, uh, really, uh, claim that it never happened.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I wanted, also, for future generations to see, that even though we went through hell-- through very difficult, terribly disturbing times and were at the pit, there is always hope.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There is always the possibility for change, especially for young people who are desperate for some reason, justifiably.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I wanted to show them, here I am.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I became an educator.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I became a parent.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I raised a family.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I still have faith in people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I still have hope for the future.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I still love people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It's important to know, and-- that there is always a change in life.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Don't ever despair because it's the end of the rope.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There's always a change, and there's also a rebirth that you don't destroy everything.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There's always a spark of life that with kindness of people, and with open mind, you can change.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I also wanted to show the world, and especially young people-- I go to schools and I talked about it-- that hate and prejudice are extremely dangerous.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they completely, um, disturb a person to see life as it could be and as it is.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And it is very important to uproot it.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
